description:
Job Highlights

Fun, young, and joyful working environment
Create ideas & improve designs for Manner Group
Coordinate with art and creative team

Responsibilities:

Copywriting or creating content and script for social media platforms
Handle production and sales project and creative, pre-production, on location shooting and post-production;
Work with Director and Production team to make sure project on time and within budget;
Time management, able to meet tight deadlines and work independently under pressure in fast paced environment;
Keep the team in a good production atmosphere
Requirements:

Three to five years of the production company or producer experience is preferred;
Able to plan independently, to coordinate, organize, and screen projects, and be familiar with the program production process;
Work experience in online marketing, social media group will be preferred;
Knowledge of production software; after Effects, Photoshop and Illustrator etc.;
Have a passion for the Internet or film industry, with enthusiasm, initiative, team awareness and coordination and strong resistance;
Work with Production Team

職位要求:

至少三至五年以上製作公司創作經驗; 獨立統籌，創作影片包括前中後期製作；篩選項目; 熟悉製作流程，有豐富影視製作，凝聚團隊，有應變能力處理突發危機，協作劇本和拍攝要求策劃拍攝.

To apply, please send us your resume / CV to us. Personal data collected will be used for recruitment purposes only.

Responsibilities :


Work closely with designers, project managers and developer
Deliver and maintain high quality interface implementation to enable a great user experience.  
Own the products’ interface implementation (HTML, CSS, presentational JS) and work with other teams to maintain a style guide for others to reference. 

Requirements :

Higher Diploma or above in Computer Science, Software Engineering, Multimedia design or other relevant disciplines;
A minimum of 1 years’ experiences in web development;
Proficiency in HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript framework like Vue.js, React, jQuery, next.js/ nuxt.js;
Well understanding in Nodejs/ JavaScript, Typescript is plus;
Basic understanding of server-side CSS pre-processing platforms, such as LESS and SASS;
Solid Experience with modern browser compatible responsive layout;
Experience with RESTful API integration and version control through GIT;
Independent, self-disciplined, well communication, responsible, good problem solving skill and a good team player;
Immediately available is preferable; 

Salary and benefit will commensurate with qualifications and experience. 
We offer 5-day work, competitive remuneration package & good career opportunities to the qualified candidate.

Interested parties, please send your full resume with current and expected salary to us via Email.

 
What You Will Be Doing:


Deliver design tasks for ATL / BTL creative marketing purposes;
Work closely with different project teams to plan, develop, execute and implement 360 creative projects;
Prepare and coordinate material for creative pitching proposals;
Provide general administrative and clerical support to the team;
Any ad-hoc tasks assigned 

 What You Need for this Position:


CREATIVE MIND with STRONG AESTHETIC SENSE
Degree holder in Advertising, Creative Media, Graphic Design or related disciplines;
Proficiency in Adobe Photoshop, Illustration is a must;
Proficiency in Adobe After Effect, Premiere is a huge advantage
With Knowledge in Cinema 4D, Blender is a advantage;
Able to organize and prioritize workload to meet deadlines;
Passionate and familiar with social media e.g. Facebook, Instagram, YouTube
Immediate available is preferred.
Online portfolio is highly preferred; 

Benefits We Offer:

5 days’ work
Performance Bonus
Medical Coverage
Flexible Working Hours
Overtime Meal and Transportation allowance
Birthday, Wedding, Maternity and Paternity leaves
Fun, young and joyful environment with lots of social activities e.g. sport games, retreat, festivals’ celebrations etc.

Be a GURU, be our next great hire. APPLY NOW!

Interested parties please send a cover letter stating your expected salary, resume and a full set of your portfolio to us

*All information will be treated as confidential and used solely for recruitment purposes.
